about the new gestalt team. It is not yet decided if they are part of 
a new faction or an existing one. Those who want to be a part of it, 
please send me a private mail msg by Friday. I'll reply and give 
indications to the 5 first person (or less if this number is lower) 
who answered this call. Again, please reply to this one privately to 
me. Thanks!
